name: Akash Bhairab
shortLoreBlurb: Akash Bhairab is a deity from Nepal tied to sky bhairab, warrior. Myths connect them with tempests and rulership.
overlapsLinks: Athena (Greek), Indra (Vedic), Karttikeya (Hindu), Perun (Slavic), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Thor (Norse), Zeus (Greek)
